The paper deals with knowledge representation and reasoning, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It specifically focuses on logic programming, which falls under the category of mathematical logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the transformation of nested logic programs into disjunctive logic programs, which is a topic in programming languages and compilers (cs.PL) and computational logic (cs.CL). Finally, the paper mentions the implementation of a compiler, which involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
